        <p class="c-landing-testimonial__position"> HR Manager at foodpanda</p>
      </div>
      <div class="item c-landing-testimonial__carousel-item">
        <div class="media c-landing-testimonial__img-container">
          <img class="c-landing-testimonial__img img-circle" src="{{url_base}}DIGEST(/images/michal-franczak-vimeda.png)">
        </div>
        <p class="c-landing-testimonial__text">Thanks to Honeypot and their match-making process, we were able to hire our Frontend Developer in only 8 days!</p>
